<A>__{the ambulance men come out of the house carrying the stretcher... there is a body on it covered by a sheet. mark raises his cine camera and photographs them. he photographs the ambulance as it drives off. he photographs the policemen dispersing the crowd. he photographs his interrogator, who gladly poses for him. then he slings his camera over his shoulder, and strolls away.}
